        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p>
                <add>היום יום ו"ו רשג ויום ב חנוכה</add>
            </p>
            <p>Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Mr Cohen</persName> will hand you this, I <sic>realy</sic>
                have nothing<lb/> what I know of any acct to write nor any news but that we<lb/> are
                all well, and last <date>Tuesday</date>
                <persName>Mr &amp; Mrs E. J. Cohen</persName>
                <sic>Dined</sic><lb/> with us and we all <sic>Drank</sic> a Bumper on acct of the
                    <sic>aprroching</sic><lb/> Birth day of yours, and I hope you will
                    <sic>Live</sic> many a year <sic>Happy</sic><lb/> and prosperous, the
                    <sic>wether</sic> is to day <sic>liek</sic> a summer day, and<lb/> have hardly
                any <sic>accation</sic> for fire <sic>accept</sic> to <sic>Roast</sic> the
                    <sic>Turkey</sic><lb/> no other news but Remain your friend x x</p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">Zalma Rehine</persName>
            </p>
            <p>all the familia send <sic>there</sic>
                <sic>Love</sic> so does <persName>Simah</persName><lb/>
                <persName>Mr &amp; Mrs E Cohen</persName> and all the rest of your friends</p>
            <pb n="2V"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">The Rev<hi rend="sup">d</hi><addressee> Isaac
                Leeser</addressee></p>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>Favour<hi rend="sup">d</hi> by</p>
            <p>the <persName>Rev<hi rend="sup">d</hi> Abraham Cohen</persName></p>
        </body>
